{"prompt": "Generate a website for a SaaS product. The website should be artistic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>AuraFlow - Flow with Clarity</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #4a90e2; /* Deep, artistic blue */\n            --secondary-color: #a0c4e8; /* Lighter, complementary blue */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1e1e1e; /* Dark background for artistic feel */\n            --accent-color: #f8f8f8;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden; /* Prevent horizontal scroll */\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-left: auto;\n            margin-right: auto;\n        }\n\n        .feature-section {\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .feature-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color) 0%, var(--primary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .cta-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-section p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        /* Artistic touch: Subtle background animation */\n        @keyframes gradientBG {\n            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }\n            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }\n            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }\n        }\n\n        .header-animation {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 50%, var(--primary-color) 100%);\n            background-size: 200% 200%;\n            animation: gradientBG 15s ease infinite;\n        }\n\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for Icons (optional, but adds visual appeal) -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"header-animation\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>AuraFlow</h1>\n            <p>Unleash your creativity and streamline your workflow with intuitive design and powerful features.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"feature-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Experience the AuraFlow Difference</h2>\n            <div class=\"features\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-paint-brush\"></i>\n                    <h3>Intuitive Interface</h3>\n                    <p>Navigate complex tasks with ease through our beautifully crafted and user-friendly design.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    <h3>Intelligent Automation</h3>\n                    <p>Let AuraFlow handle the repetitive tasks, so you can focus on what truly matters.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                    <h3>Seamless Collaboration</h3>\n                    <p>Work together with your team in real-time, no matter where you are.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-rocket\"></i>\n                    <h3>Scalable Solutions</h3>\n                    <p>From startups to enterprises, AuraFlow grows with your ambitions.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Ready to Transform Your Workflow?</h2>\n            <p>Join thousands of innovators who are already experiencing the future of productivity.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Start Your Free Trial</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 AuraFlow. All rights reserved. | <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add some subtle animations on scroll if desired, or keep it simple.\n        // For this example, we'll keep the JS minimal.\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}